        <updateDate>2021-09-10T18:33:22Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Forcing Limits on Abusive and Tumultuous Prices or the FLAT Prices Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Food and Drug Administration to reduce the market exclusivity of an approved prescription drug if the drug manufacturer increases the drug's price by more than a specified percentage. This reduction may be waived under specified circumstances.<br /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
